text: Edmore Sibanda (born 3 June 1984) is a Zimbabwean footballer. He plays as a goalkeeper for Golden Arrows. He also plays for the Zimbabwe national football team. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:2019 Africa Cup of Nations players Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers
